cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.DC, cs.MA 

This paper deals with the problem of providing quality of service in multihop wireless networks, which is a topic related to network protocols and communication systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves optimization techniques and distributed algorithms, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper uses the theory of fluid limits of queues, which is a topic related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and mathematical analysis (cs.MA).
